                "core_idea": "【核心思路】极值点 $x_0=e$。目标证 $x_1 x_2 > e^2 \\iff \\ln x_1 + \\ln x_2 > 2$。利用 $\\frac{\\ln x_1}{x_1} = \\frac{\\ln x_2}{x_2} = a$，采用比值代换 $t = x_2/x_1$。",
                "key_steps": [
                  "1. 极值点分析：",
                  "   $f'(x) = \\frac{1-\\ln x}{x^2}$。令 $f'(x)=0 \\Rightarrow x_0=e$。",
                  "   $x \\in (0, e)$ 增，$x \\in (e, +\\infty)$ 减。",
                  "2. 转化目标：",
                  "   需证 $x_1 x_2 > e^2$，两边取对数即证 $\\ln x_1 + \\ln x_2 > 2$。",
