                  "   令 $t = \\frac{x_2}{x_1}$，因 $x_1 < e < x_2$，故 $t > 1$。",
                  "   由 $f(x_1)=f(x_2)=a$ 得 $\\frac{\\ln x_1}{x_1} = \\frac{\\ln x_2}{x_2}$。",
                  "   代入 $x_2 = t x_1$：$\\frac{\\ln x_1}{x_1} = \\frac{\\ln (t x_1)}{t x_1} = \\frac{\\ln t + \\ln x_1}{t x_1}$。",
                  "   化简得：$t \\ln x_1 = \\ln t + \\ln x_1 \\Rightarrow (t-1)\\ln x_1 = \\ln t$。",
                  "   解得：$\\ln x_1 = \\frac{\\ln t}{t-1}$。",
                  "4. 表示 $\\ln x_2$：",
                  "   $\\ln x_2 = \\ln (t x_1) = \\ln t + \\ln x_1 = \\ln t + \\frac{\\ln t}{t-1} = \\frac{t \\ln t}{t-1}$。",
                  "5. 构建单变量函数：",
                  "   目标和 $S = \\ln x_1 + \\ln x_2 = \\frac{(t+1)\\ln t}{t-1}$。",
