                  "   两式相减：$\\ln x_1 - \\ln x_2 = a(x_1 - x_2)$。",
                  "   得 $a = \\frac{\\ln x_1 - \\ln x_2}{x_1 - x_2}$。",
                  "2. 转化目标不等式：",
                  "   需证 $x_1+x_2 > \\frac{2}{a} = \\frac{2(x_1-x_2)}{\\ln x_1 - \\ln x_2}$。",
