                  "   当 $t>1$ 时，$h''(t) > 0 \\Rightarrow h'(t)$ 递增。",
                  "   $h'(t) > h'(1) = 0$。",
                  "   故 $h(t)$ 递增，$h(t) > h(1) = 0$。",
